    "extras": [
      "Visa: Turkish e-Visa is about ₹4,285 at evisa.gov.tr; keep a printout with your passport.",
      "Museum Pass Istanbul is about ₹3,640 for 5 days and pays off quickly if you are doing Topkapi and the archaeology museums.",
      "Museum Pass Cappadocia is about ₹5,200 for 3 days and covers Göreme and Zelve area sites.",
      "Pick up an İstanbulkart on day 1 (about ₹260 deposit) for cheaper metro, tram, and ferry rides.",
      "Vegetarian staples that are easy to find: mercimek çorbası, gözleme, simit, imam bayıldı, meze plates, and peynirli pide.",
